@siflower Probably. For the IV arbitrage, it’s on the tail end on IV expansion but still a good opportunity with $EWY.

IV 45% does not move 6% a day, especially before 10x perps and 2x leverage ETFs come out.

That being said Korean index will likely keep going up and maybe double. Sk Hynix is making more than Google in 2027 and is valued at like 1/9th the mc.

